":"已經有人比公安屈佢帶槍過關<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGood Luck man<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b41c0ce8a197b8d2ebd7bbf7c09e21408de02b4","tid":1499353,"uid":110939,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:55:06.000Z","msg":"我每日公幹都要過關，過親都check 硬，無論你出境定入境，只要係男又後後生生8，9成都要check。（女都有機會，通常都係一班frd ,男女朋友，所以迫住一齊check埋）<br />\nCheck 野最基本起碼要查背囊，問下你咩名，黎大陸做咩，你做邊行。<br />\n如果佢覺得少少可疑，或係香港人大多數都要睇埋手機，主要睇你相簿，有冇關遊行資訊。所以如果你有就del曬佢（最近刪除都要清空）生活照就留底做下樣。通常做到咁已經放你走。 <br />\n不過，佢真係睇你唔順會check 埋你WhatsApp 或其他社交網絡。 睇你群組對話記錄，最好都係咩都del曬佢，唔好比佢知你有發夢之類。就應該完全沒問題"},{"pid":"b5440967041ebff75af1e62450a2f5b5b4c11632","tid":1499353,"uid":90883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:56:37.000Z","msg":"弱智 打緊仗入敵人陣地"},{"pid":"4c18aee758a60dfa2a257432e91ac31b05075770","tid":1499353,"uid":223431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:04:19.000Z","msg":"去澳門會唔會有事?"},{"pid":"15fd333c05853b622e0add1b2b70c216efb16276","tid":1499353,"uid":167394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:05:05.000Z","msg":"多D愛國人相<br />\n申請定假FACEBOOK 全部愛國愛港"},{"pid":"c0292ce9d1af87db9bcf13ffba4c015fa47189ee","tid":1499353,"uid":41961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49a7660bfa8c7a6aa49bad9323c4e3a72fb3e40","tid":1499353,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2197d8f28f789f1081c7b10cee48b9e8d7f34a86","tid":1499353,"uid":193220,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"012cdad0fd203ac8bebd607a494fc6802dc34bda","tid":1499353,"uid":2419,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:27:11.000Z","msg":"唔好撚去"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:27:38